            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "metadata": {},
                    "children": [],
                    "content": [
                        "When converting data between two mediums that are largely dissimilar, it often helps to create an intermediate representation of data. In this case, our data “pipeline” could look something like:"
